OL,3,CMichael Beale sacked by Sunderland
OL,4,Cafter 63 days in charge
OL,6,FSunderland have confirmed they have
OL,7,Fparted company with head coach Michael
OL,8,FBeale.
OL,10,FThe 43-year-old spent just 63 days on
OL,11,FWearside and departs with the club
OL,12,Fsitting tenth in the Championship,
OL,13,Fwinning four of the eleven league
OL,14,Fgames since he took charge.
OL,16,FHis tenure also included a 3-0 defeat
OL,17,Fto fierce local rivals Newcastle in
OL,18,Fthe FA Cup third round, in their first
OL,19,Fencounter for almost eight years.
