OL,3,CMichael Beale sacked by Sunderland
OL,4,Cafter 63 days in charge
OL,6,FAnnouncing Beale's dismissal, a
OL,7,Fstatement from the club's sporting
OL,8,Fdirector, Kristjaan Speakman, said:
OL,9,F"We are disappointed that Michael is
OL,10,Fleaving Sunderland AFC.
OL,12,F"Our desire is to improve and
OL,13,Funfortunately that hasn't been
OL,14,Fevident, as such we take full
OL,15,Faccountability and feel that acting
OL,16,Fdecisively is in the best interests of
OL,17,Fthe club.
OL,19,F"This has been a difficult few months
OL,20,Ffor Michael, who leaves with our best
OL,21,Fwishes for the future."
