OL,3,CMichael Beale sacked by Sunderland
OL,4,Cafter 63 days in charge
OL,6,FMike Dodds, who previously served as
OL,7,Fcaretaker manager this season when
OL,8,FTony Mowbray was sacked, will resume
OL,9,Fcontrol until the end of the season.
OL,11,FWatch what people in Sunderland had to
OL,12,Fsay following the announcement.
OL,14,FMr Speakman continued: "Our focus is
OL,15,Fnow on the players and supporting Mike
OL,16,FDodds in the remaining games to ensure
OL,17,Fwe achieve the highest possible league
OL,18,Ffinish.
