OL,6,F"We will be updating our supporters
OL,7,Ffurther as and when significant
OL,8,Fdevelopments are made."
OL,10,FBeale's appointment was met with an
OL,11,Funderwhelming response from Sunderland
OL,12,Ffans when it was announced in December.
OL,14,FHis final game in charge saw
OL,15,FSunderland lose 2-1 to Birmingham City
OL,16,Fas Mowbray claimed victory over the
OL,17,Fman who he was replaced by.
